OL,3,CCommunity hub's rallying call to save
OL,4,Cthe building
OL,6,FVolunteers, parents, and young people
OL,7,Fhave all taken part in fundraising
OL,8,Fefforts, including car washes and a
OL,9,Fsponsored "skip-a-thon", and a raffle.
OL,11,FAfter raising #17,000 over the course
OL,12,Fof a month, Derbyshire County Council
OL,13,Fgranted a three-month postponement of
OL,14,Ftheir decision to close the centre to
OL,15,Fallow volunteers time to raise the
OL,16,Fnecessary funds.
OL,18,FGamesley, in the High Peak, is one of
OL,19,Fthe most deprived areas in the country.
