OL,3,CCommunity hub's rallying call to save
OL,4,Cthe building
OL,6,FThe estate was built in the 1960s as
OL,7,Fpart of the slum clearances of
OL,8,FManchester.
OL,10,FIts origins lie as a Roman fort
OL,11,Frenamed 'Melandra'- which also lends
OL,12,Fits name to the road surrounding the
OL,13,Festate.
OL,15,FSince 2010, funding from youth
OL,16,Fservices have been cut by over 76% in
OL,17,Fthe region, signalling concern in the
OL,18,Fyouth work profession.
