OL,3,CCommunity hub's rallying call to save
OL,4,Cthe building
OL,6,F"The community is going to be very
OL,7,Fdemotivated. They already feel
OL,8,Fundervalued so that's just going to
OL,9,Fget worse. The inequalities on the
OL,10,Festate will grow if we don't do what
OL,11,Fwe're planning on doing."
OL,13,FThe community has until the end of
OL,14,FJune to raise the funds.
